examples.en: He peeped his head through the window.
I peeped my head out from under the blanket.
The door was ajar and Helen peeped in.
I peeped through the keyhole and watched them.
He peeped inquisitively into the drawer.
The stars peeped out as the clouds hurried past.
He peeped at the woman through the window.
The new moon peeped through the tree tops.
She opened the door a crack and peeped into the room.
When her knock elicited no response, she opened the door and peeped in.
